title: God Has The Right People In Your Future | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: God Has The Right People In Your Future | Joel Osteen
description:
God is orchestrating your life down to the smallest detail. He knows how to get you to the people you need to fulfill your destiny.

 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
